quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  8,1,"Bakhurebanga omwandu kunyoolelwe mwiyie (kukabwe kurie). Boola mbu, “Omwandu kunyoolelwe mwiyie ni kwa Nyasaye nende Omurumwa (londe shingala betsa okhubakaba). Kho rie Nyasaye, ne kasie omulembe hakari wenyu, ne wulile Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe ni muli Abasuubili (abahabwene)."
  8,2,"Toto Abasuubili ba habwene, nibalia olwa Nyasaye arumbulwa, emioyo chiabu chitsulamwo oburi, ne nibasomelwa tsinyaali tsiefu, tsibameta obusuubili, ne Nyasaye wabu Omulesi butswa niye wabesikanga."
  8,3,"Balia abalamanga khatsotso (iswala), ne khushia khubakabile, bahananga eshihanwa."
  8,4,"Abo nibo abasuubili batoto. Bali nende tsingasi (obukhongo) ewa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, nende eshileshelo, nende omukabo kwoluyali."
  8,5,"Shinga olwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yakhurusia munzu yiyio khubwatoto. Ne toto omukanda mulala mubasuubili shikwali nikuchamile tawe."
  8,6,"Bakhuyingasinjia akobwatoto, nako nikamalile okhurumbukha, opara mbu balumungwa okhutsia mulumbe nibalola."
  8,7,"Ne olwa Nyasaye yabalaka mbu omukanda mulala kulaba okwenyu mumikanda chibili chilia, nanyu mwali muyanzile munyoole omukanda kubula amawa kube okwenyu. Ne Nyasaye yenya okhura habulafu obwatoto khumakhuwa keke, ne atete emisi chia abakhayi."
  8,8,"Kho anyoole okhwemia obulaamba, ne akwisie hasi obubeyi, kata ababii nibasinyikha."